name: GoSon
tagline: GSON ! aka JSON to GO struct
body:
### Welcome to the JSON to GO challenge 
This is my stab at Go . If you like it awesome if not 'Go fmt yer self!'. Just kidding but seriously. 

```
$ git clone https://github.com/RBdevelop/GoSon/
$ Serve over basil and enjoy! 
```




### Authors and Contributors
The humble attempt of @rbdevelop with pointers from @bpeters and slap of wisdom from @GeertJohan

### Support or Contact
Having trouble running this on your local? Go get Help (pun intended) No just email robert@rbdevelop.com and I can debug.
